</p><p class="- topic/p ">On the operator panel, tap on the [System] icon on the right. Tap on [Power management]. Tap on [Power off]. The system shuts down. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Switch off the power supply</b>: 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">When the system has shut down, pull to open the cover under the roll winder. Switch the power switch to the 'off' position. 
</p></li><li id="LI_3A6A780FCE62425DA268B914DC7D2D21" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Open the ink system. 
